    /*                    RECOVERY OPERATIONS                     */
    /*.•°:°.´+˚.*°.˚:*.´•*.+°.•°:´*.´•*.•°.•°:°.´:•˚°.*°.˚:*.´+°.•*/

    /// @dev Recovers the signer's address from a message digest `hash`, and the `signature`.
    function recover(bytes32 hash, bytes memory signature) internal view returns (address result) {
